pan class=title> Some advice.</span><hr size=1>   If you kill me by pulling mobs through where I'm fighting, don't get surprised if I get annoyed, tell you &quot;I'm too angry to discuss this at the moment&quot;, and arrange my own corpse retrieval / ressurection.<br>
<br>
  Don't keep trying to justify yourself to me.  You just -killed- me.  Of course I'm going to be angry at you.  I'm not going to send you abusive tells or anything of that nature, but if you keep bugging me after I've told you that I'm not interested in discussing it right now I'm going to tell you EXACTLY what I think of people who are inconsiderate enough to pull through me, aggro a Lava Guardian on me, and cause me to loose experience through no fault of my own.  <br>
<br>
  And sure as hell pray that neither you, or the guild that condones your actions ever need any help, or benefit of the doubt, from me.  Because sure as hell I'm going to remember you, your actions, and your utter lack of responsibility in the future. <br>
<br>
  Oh, and placing me on your /ignore list when I'm only responding to tells that you made -after- I told you I was not interested in discussing the matter is amusing.  I liked that touch, was almost as if you'd convinced yourself that you were in the right.<br>
<br>
